      <div class="col-8" style="font-size: 12px; color: #0080ff; padding-top: 2px;">
        <span style="color: #003366">Basic features for your trail, with sensors, dimmer, light, shade, video doorbell, a Universal Voice Control (UVC) and optional fan, coffe maker or toaster.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <br>
  <a href="apps/package?package=<%=data[1][0] %>">
    <div class="row" style="padding: 10px; border: 0px solid #003366; margin:0  auto; height: 80px; width: 400px; ">
      <div class="col-4" style="font-size: 20px; background-image: url(images/<%=data[1][0] %>.jpg); padding-top: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill">$2000+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8" style="font-size: 12px; color: #0080ff; padding-top: 2px;">
        <span style="color: #003366">Standard features for a whole-house solution with a display screen and 2-way intercom and more sensors, switches, plugs, dimmers and lights.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <br>
  <a href="apps/package?package=<%=data[2][0] %>">
    <div class="row" style="padding: 10px; border: 0px solid #003366; margin: 0 auto; height: 80px; width: 400px; ">
      <div class="col-4" style="font-size: 20px; background-image: url(images/<%=data[2][0] %>.jpg); padding-top: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <span class="badge badge-primary badge-pill">$5000+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8" style="font-size:12px; color: #0080ff; padding-top: 2px;">
        <span style="color: #003366">Premium features with additional options available for doollock, garage opener, themostat and a display screen on the refrigerator.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <p>
  <div class="text-center" style="font-size:14px;">
    <div class="p-1" style="color: #003366">
      <p>Or you can <a href="apps/level1">customize</a> it by picking up from <br>
        <a href="apps/level2?i=0&level1=Rooms">Rooms</a>,
        <a href="apps/level2?i=0&level1=Scene">Scene</a> and
        <a href="apps/level2?i=0&level1=Devices">Devices</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
